{"tid":1761702,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［行動POST] 今晚7點 理工 和你school","createTime":"2019-11-29T05:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T03:04:41.000Z","uid":236518,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5f6a8ab23dd928257d6c5cce63cdbba3d37e12f5","tid":1761702,"uid":236518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"雖然poly冇晒人足，但係既然重開校園，不如收工一齊入去清潔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1761039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1761039</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思呀上個post開得太差<br />\n是咁的，<br />\n小弟半個月前漏左野係理大，<br />\n想大家幫手搵下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢地有機會入晒隨意門，但驚有漏網之魚，大家可唔可以幫下手呀<br />\n去完理工再一齊去做鄭文傑啦<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示：<br />\n天氣凍啦，著多幾件衫呀<br />\n如果理工唔入得就係門口/紅磡行街食飯啦<br />\n總之要人<br />\n終極和理非<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外幫拜托大家整張文宣圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9578c1f02e764f9953569f1a61fba3f87e4ea556","tid":1761702,"uid":236518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:33:17.000Z","msg":"天氣凍啦"},{"pid":"621459775cdee51f84c8fed4bf452983511abe4c","tid":1761702,"uid":236518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:33:41.000Z","msg":"poly又解封"},{"pid":"0573f1bf89d19efde5bd7e4d7f7d63c45e7cc232","tid":1761702,"uid":236518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:35:13.000Z","msg":"入去行下街"},{"pid":"44815d562342b90235ee1a338f33fbd0f3974cc9","tid":1761702,"uid":236518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:35:26.000Z","msg":"換下衫"},{"pid":"37caff950c066cd53c4f5b40b652245bc9e6a57f","tid":1761702,"uid":236518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"